<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:42
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='391017' id='t-391017'>And you might be thinking, well, you know,</span>
