<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='466259' id='t-466259'>And so what these studies are showing</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='468560' id='t-468560'>is that when you feed people misinformation</span>
