<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='556423' id='t-556423'>that could have supported her story.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='559304' id='t-559304'>And when I began looking into these cases,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='562312' id='t-562312'>I was wondering,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='563762' id='t-563762'>where do these bizarre memories come from?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='566090' id='t-566090'>And what I found is that most of these situations</span>
