<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='730287' id='t-730287'>Well, to my surprise,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='733325' id='t-733325'>when I published this work and began to speak out</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='736754' id='t-736754'>against this particular brand of psychotherapy,</span>
