<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='838836' id='t-838836'>When I got back to my work, I asked this question:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='842194' id='t-842194'>if I plant a false memory in your mind,</span>
